<hymn_number>2016</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 tḥmlny ydạh wtʿtny ṭwl ạlzmạn
 wfy ṭryq kẖyr yqwd syry kl ận
 fy ạllyl wạlnhạr yḥyṭ by str ạlạ̉mạn
 flạ ạ̉kẖạf sẖrạaⁿ yswʿ ykfyny ḍmạn
 ạlqrạr - tḥmlny ydạh ... tstrny dmạh ... yạ̉srny ḥb yswʿ
 tstrny dmạh wbrh ywm ạlḥsạb
 mhmạ ṭmt dẖnwby wlw ʿlt fwq ạlsḥạb
 mạ dmt fy ạlmsyḥ flst ạ̉kẖsẖy̱ mn ʿqạb
 wʿndmạ yrạ̉ny lạ lwm ạ̉w ḥty̱ ʿtạb
 yạ̉srny ḥnạn wnʿmh tsby ạlkyạn
 flst mstḥqạaⁿ fy byth ạ̉y mkạn
 lknh ʿjyb wḥbh fwq ạlbyạn
 wḥbh sybqy̱ ạ̉nsẖwdty ṭwl ạlzmạn</lyrics>
<title>tḥmlny ydạh</title>
</song>